> You said 'for Windows here serial' but a SerialParam() just runs lapply and would not have problems finding f

Ah, I assumed that the registry under Windows would also have a MulticoreParam as default which would then dispatch to a SerialParam -- but I now see that it actually has a SnowParam as default. Even better!

Thanks a lot,
